For more information on Mr. Terrific and DC All In, follow @DCOfficial on social media (@[dc.com](http://dc.com/) on Bluesky) and visit the DC All In hub at [https://www.dc.com/allin](https://www.dc.com/allin). Fans can also discover and relive some of Mr. Terrific’s greatest moments, including the 2011 _Mister Terrific_ limited series, _Justice Society of America_, _The Terrifics_ (from DC’s New Age of Heroes)_,_ and Tom King and Mitch Gerads’ bestselling _Strange Adventures_, with a subscription to the DC UNIVERSE INFINITE (DCUI) digital subscription platform. For more information and a free trial, visit the DCUI website at [https://www.dcuniverseinfinite.com](https://www.dcuniverseinfinite.com/). DCUI is not available in all countries and is not intended for children.